Key Match Events: Australia came from behind to beat China 3-1
Goals from Lewis Miller, Craig Goodwin, and Nishan Velupillay secured the win
Pre-Game Insights: Tony Popovic replaced Graham Arnold as coach
Australia had a shock 1-0 home loss to Bahrain and a scoreless draw in Indonesia prior to this match
Post-Match Reflections: Socceroos skipper Jackson Irvine praised the team's composure after losing the first goal
Tony Popovic's reign as coach started with a win
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was played in front of almost 50,000 fans at Adelaide Oval
